Data visualization
========================================================

The `ggplot` function "opens" the data and the `geom` function specifies the type of plot with the variables that will be used.

The general structure is like this:

```{r, echo=T, eval = F}
ggplot(data = <DATA>) + 
  <GEOM_FUNCTION>(mapping = aes(<MAPPINGS>))
```

